    <briefdescription>
<para>Subclass of <ref refid="classgodot_1_1_vision_server" kindref="compound">VisionServer</ref> enabling manual frame injection for unit testing and virtualization. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classgodot_1_1_mock_vision_server" kindref="compound">MockVisionServer</ref> overrides camera capture logic to return manually injected textures rather than reading from a physical webcam. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
